faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然唔係我果個答案，但你又啱喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n試下估埋我個答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f66753e39612420f3404b104f44a9ca9d45abb9b","tid":347240,"uid":93940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T16:22:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死魚，因為死魚做愛唔出聲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但無端端關 做愛 咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84afa2a9b273bed4c79ca2ae21ae64082b11e61e","tid":347240,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T16:39:00.000Z","msg":"樓主不如開估 想睇下你個答案有幾高質"},{"pid":"a45d205fa34ec80ed3f2b275c618a441bc595c36","tid":347240,"uid":93940,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:13:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主不如開估 想睇下你個答案有幾高質</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好呀，多謝你既支持。<br />\n<br />\n我本身諗到既答案係 敢怒不敢言 既 敢怒雲吞 (錦滷餛飩 既 同音字)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">(原理同 花式溜冰、英式桌球 一樣係食字，或者而家已經唔興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</span></span><br />\n<br />\n題目個重點在於「唔敢」呢兩個字，所以我篩走左「講唔出聲」。<br />\n<br />\n而「沉默是柑」同「默不作聲」既墨魚 係 思路接近。<br />\n<br />\n當然，朱國忠 巴打 既 鵪鶉 係高質既，我真係無諗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2db807422a8bc69ef415dd0beaae9169db14ee","tid":347240,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:17:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主不如開估 想睇下你個答案有幾高質</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好呀，多謝你既支持。<br />\n<br />\n我本身諗到既答案係 敢怒不敢言 既 敢怒雲吞 (錦滷餛飩 既 同音字)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">(原理同 花式溜冰、英式桌球 一樣係食字，或者而家已經唔興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</span></span><br />\n<br />\n題目個重點在於「唔敢」呢兩個字，所以我篩走左「講唔出聲」。<br />\n<br />\n而「沉默是柑」同「默不作聲」既墨魚 係 思路接近。<br />\n<br />\n當然，朱國忠 巴打 既 鵪鶉 係高質既，我真係無諗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本身想屌你，但見你咁好心機打出黎又唔算低質。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d4de81ea43c066b9c1c15fb4bb8edbef2c946e2","tid":347240,"uid":121771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:20:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>死魚，因為死魚做愛唔出聲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但無端端關 做愛 咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你食緊條女嗰陣時， 心裏面*佢 死魚唔出聲"},{"pid":"cd62e0e289409d20fa64b2c47f37ede70521428a","tid":347240,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:21:01.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f85db6d257bac218008091dcba541a844aefc21f","tid":347240,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:26:30.000Z","msg":"留名等睇你開估比人屌<br />\n我就唔屌你住，廢事炒車"},{"pid":"096f861605b057e241b0ad3c6ba26cb5d42bd58c","tid":347240,"uid":93940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T03:50:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>死魚，因為死魚做愛唔出聲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但無端端關 做愛 咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你食緊條女嗰陣時， 心裏面*佢 死魚唔出聲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可惜條女係唔會出聲，而唔係唔敢出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr